 href=''http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~3/zxlD_rF5-rc/terry-sutton-on-contributing-to-wordpress'' title=''Terry Sutton shares his experience on contributing to WordPress 3.5. I wonder how many other newcomers to WordPress feel the same way or have gone through the same struggles as Terry. Hopefully, most of his issues along with everyone else’s will be addressed in the Core Contributors handbook. No related posts. [&hellip;]''>WPTavern: Terry Sutton On Contributing To WordPress</a></li></ul></div>', 'no');
